**Usage**: Any component can push notifications:
```tsx
import { useNotificationStore } from '@/stores/notification.store'

const { addNotification } = useNotificationStore()
addNotification({ type: 'success', title: 'TPS Added', message: 'TPS 05 has been created' })
```

